data.description: Buy this Home and We'll Buy yours!* OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 2/17 1:00 TO 2:00 PM! Situated in the charming Settlers Village, it presents a captivating two-story residence. This home has six bedrooms and four bathrooms spread across 2,863 square feet and ample space for comfortable living. The finished basement provides additional flexibility and utility to suit various needs. One of the standout features of this property is its spacious kitchen, adorned with granite countertops. Stainless steel appliances are all included. The formal dining room complements this setup, offering an elegant setting for entertainment.  Also off the kitchen is a large family room with a cozy fireplace. This space is ideal for relaxation and socializing, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for residents and guests alike. A focal point of the home is the living room, accentuated by a picturesque window that invites in natural light and provides scenic views. Outside, the private yard offers a serene retreat where one can unwind and appreciate the outdoors. There is central air, washer and dryer included.  Close to I-25, shopping, light rail. 1-year APHW for the buyer is included! *Cond. apply!
